            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EEzra%20realized%20that%20if%20he%20tolerated%20the%20intermarriage%20of%20Israelites%20with%20foreign%20women%2C%20eventually%20the%20holy%20seed%20would%20become%20extinct%20and%20the%20Messiah%20would%20never%20come%20(Ezra%209%3A2).%20Just%20as%20Ezra%20was%20appalled%20at%20the%20Israelites'%20terrible%20breach%20of%20God's%20law%2C%20Paul%20was%20equally%20horrified%20that%20sin%20had%20crept%20into%20the%20church%20at%20Corinth.%20He%20ordered%20the%20excommunication%20of%20the%20one%20who%20was%20in%20open%2C%20unrepentant%20sin%20so%20that%20the%20Body%20of%20Christ%20could%20participate%20in%20a%20pure%20Passover%20feast.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EJust%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20yeast%20will%20cause%20the%20dough%20to%20rise%2C%20and%20a%20little%20sin%20mixed%20into%20a%20church%20will%20cause%20it%20to%20be%20filled%20with%20the%20%22bread%20of%20wickedness%20and%20evil%22%20(1%20Corinthians%205%3A8).%20We%20must%20separate%20ourselves%20from%20any%20so-called%20brother%20who%20continues%20to%20sin%20through%20immorality%2C%20greed%2C%20thievery%2C%20or%20idolatry.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ESeparating%20ourselves%20from%20unrepentant%20sin%20benefits%20not%20only%20us%20but%20also%20the%20whole%20Church.%20The%20end%20result%3F%20The%20Church%20will%20be%20protected%2C%20and%20perhaps%20the%20offender%20will%20repent%20and%20be%20saved%20(1%20Corinthians%205%3A5).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Ezra.8:21-9:15",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EEzra%208%3A21-9%3A15%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_8_21%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20there%20by%20the%20Ahava%20Canal%2C%20I%20gave%20orders%20for%20all%20of%20us%20to%20fast%20and%20humble%20ourselves%20before%20our%20God.%20We%20prayed%20that%20he%20would%20give%20us%20a%20safe%20journey%20and%20protect%20us%2C%20our%20children%2C%20and%20our%20goods%20as%20we%20traveled.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_8_22%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20I%20was%20ashamed%20to%20ask%20the%20king%20for%20soldiers%20and%20horsemen%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A22%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Echarioteers.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20to%20accompany%20us%20and%20protect%20us%20from%20enemies%20along%20the%20way.%20After%20all%2C%20we%20had%20told%20the%20king%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BOur%20God%26%23x2019%3Bs%20hand%20of%20protection%20is%20on%20all%20who%20worship%20him%2C%20but%20his%20fierce%20anger%20rages%20against%20those%20who%20abandon%20him.%26%23x201D%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_8_23%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20we%20fasted%20and%20earnestly%20prayed%20that%20our%20God%20would%20take%20care%20of%20us%2C%20and%20he%20heard%20our%20prayer.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_8_24%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20appointed%20twelve%20leaders%20of%20the%20priests%26%23x2014%3BSherebiah%2C%20Hashabiah%2C%20and%20ten%20other%20priests%26%23x2014%3B%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_8_25%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3Eto%20be%20in%20charge%20of%20transporting%20the%20silver%2C%20the%20gold%2C%20the%20gold%20bowls%2C%20and%20the%20other%20items%20that%20the%20king%2C%20his%20council%2C%20his%20officials%2C%20and%20all%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20had%20presented%20for%20the%20Temple%20of%20God.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_8_26%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20weighed%20the%20treasure%20as%20I%20gave%20it%20to%20them%20and%20found%20the%20totals%20to%20be%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22list-sp%22%3E24%26%23xA0%3Btons%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A26a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E650%26%23xA0%3Btalents%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B22%26%23xA0%3Bmetric%20tons%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20silver%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list%22%3E7%2C500%20pounds%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A26b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E100%26%23xA0%3Btalents%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B3%2C400%20kilograms%5D%3B%20also%20in%208%3A26c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20silver%20articles%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list%22%3E7%2C500%20pounds%20of%20gold%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_8_27%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E27%3C%2Fspan%3E20%26%23xA0%3Bgold%20bowls%2C%20equal%20in%20value%20to%201%2C000%20gold%20coins%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A27%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E1%2C000%20darics%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%2019%26%23xA0%3Bpounds%20or%208.6%26%23xA0%3Bkilograms%20in%20weight.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list%22%3E2%26%23xA0%3Bfine%20articles%20of%20polished%20bronze%2C%20as%20precious%20as%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_8_28%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E28%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20I%20said%20to%20these%20priests%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BYou%20and%20these%20treasures%20have%20been%20set%20apart%20as%20holy%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20This%20silver%20and%20gold%20is%20a%20voluntary%20offering%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20our%20ancestors.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_8_29%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E29%3C%2Fspan%3EGuard%20these%20treasures%20well%20until%20you%20present%20them%20to%20the%20leading%20priests%2C%20the%20Levites%2C%20and%20the%20leaders%20of%20Israel%2C%20who%20will%20weigh%20them%20at%20the%20storerooms%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Temple%20in%20Jerusalem.%26%23x201D%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_8_30%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2230%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E30%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20priests%20and%20the%20Levites%20accepted%20the%20task%20of%20transporting%20these%20treasures%20of%20silver%20and%20gold%20to%20the%20Temple%20of%20our%20God%20in%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_8_31%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2231%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E31%3C%2Fspan%3EWe%20broke%20camp%20at%20the%20Ahava%20Canal%20on%20April%26%23xA0%3B19%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A31%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eon%20the%20twelfth%20day%20of%20the%20first%20month%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20ancient%20Hebrew%20lunar%20calendar.%20This%20day%20was%20April%26%23xA0%3B19%2C%20458%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3Eb.c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3B%20also%20see%20note%20on%206%3A15.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20started%20off%20to%20Jerusalem.%20And%20the%20gracious%20hand%20of%20our%20God%20protected%20us%20and%20saved%20us%20from%20enemies%20and%20bandits%20along%20the%20way.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_8_32%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2232%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E32%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20we%20arrived%20safely%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20where%20we%20rested%20for%20three%20days.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_8_33%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2233%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E33%3C%2Fspan%3EOn%20the%20fourth%20day%20after%20our%20arrival%2C%20the%20silver%2C%20gold%2C%20and%20other%20valuables%20were%20weighed%20at%20the%20Temple%20of%20our%20God%20and%20entrusted%20to%20Meremoth%20son%20of%20Uriah%20the%20priest%20and%20to%20Eleazar%20son%20of%20Phinehas%2C%20along%20with%20Jozabad%20son%20of%20Jeshua%20and%20Noadiah%20son%20of%20Binnui%26%23x2014%3Bboth%20of%20whom%20were%20Levites.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_8_34%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2234%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E34%3C%2Fspan%3EEverything%20was%20accounted%20for%20by%20number%20and%20weight%2C%20and%20the%20total%20weight%20was%20officially%20recorded.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_8_35%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2235%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E35%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20exiles%20who%20had%20come%20out%20of%20captivity%20sacrificed%20burnt%20offerings%20to%20the%20God%20of%20Israel.%20They%20presented%20twelve%20bulls%20for%20all%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%2C%20as%20well%20as%20ninety-six%20rams%20and%20seventy-seven%20male%20lambs.%20They%20also%20offered%20twelve%20male%20goats%20as%20a%20sin%20offering.%20All%20this%20was%20given%20as%20a%20burnt%20offering%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_8_36%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2236%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E36%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20decrees%20were%20delivered%20to%20his%20highest%20officers%20and%20the%20governors%20of%20the%20province%20west%20of%20the%20Euphrates%20River%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A36%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20province%20beyond%20the%20river.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20who%20then%20cooperated%20by%20supporting%20the%20people%20and%20the%20Temple%20of%20God.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_9_1%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEzra%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EEzra%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Prayer%20concerning%20Intermarriage%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20these%20things%20had%20been%20done%2C%20the%20Jewish%20leaders%20came%20to%20me%20and%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BMany%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%2C%20and%20even%20some%20of%20the%20priests%20and%20Levites%2C%20have%20not%20kept%20themselves%20separate%20from%20the%20other%20peoples%20living%20in%20the%20land.%20They%20have%20taken%20up%20the%20detestable%20practices%20of%20the%20Canaanites%2C%20Hittites%2C%20Perizzites%2C%20Jebusites%2C%20Ammonites%2C%20Moabites%2C%20Egyptians%2C%20and%20Amorites.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_9_2%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20the%20men%20of%20Israel%20have%20married%20women%20from%20these%20people%20and%20have%20taken%20them%20as%20wives%20for%20their%20sons.%20So%20the%20holy%20race%20has%20become%20polluted%20by%20these%20mixed%20marriages.%20Worse%20yet%2C%20the%20leaders%20and%20officials%20have%20led%20the%20way%20in%20this%20outrage.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_9_3%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20I%20heard%20this%2C%20I%20tore%20my%20cloak%20and%20my%20shirt%2C%20pulled%20hair%20from%20my%20head%20and%20beard%2C%20and%20sat%20down%20utterly%20shocked.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_9_4%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20all%20who%20trembled%20at%20the%20words%20of%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%20came%20and%20sat%20with%20me%20because%20of%20this%20outrage%20committed%20by%20the%20returned%20exiles.%20And%20I%20sat%20there%20utterly%20appalled%20until%20the%20time%20of%20the%20evening%20sacrifice.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_9_5%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20the%20sacrifice%2C%20I%20stood%20up%20from%20where%20I%20had%20sat%20in%20mourning%20with%20my%20clothes%20torn.%20I%20fell%20to%20my%20knees%20and%20lifted%20my%20hands%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20my%20God.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_9_6%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20prayed%2C%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-fl-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3Bmy%20God%2C%20I%20am%20utterly%20ashamed%3B%20I%20blush%20to%20lift%20up%